docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. Syntax for Creating Tables in .md Name | Academy | score - | :-: | -: Harry Potter | Gryffindor| 90 Display as below: Name Academy score Harry Potter Gryffindor 90 Syntax for Uploading ZIP File in .md [File_Name](files/file.zip) Display as below: file1.zip
